        <div class="buttons">
            <button id="yesBtn" onclick="showMessage()">YES!</button>
            <button id="noBtn" onmouseover="moveButton()" onclick="moveButton()">NO</button>
        </div>
        
        <div id="message"> Hi bibiiii ! I just wanted to say that I really love you, more than words can ever truly express. You make everything brighter, and I feel so lucky to have you in my life.Hoping to make this Valentine's Day as special as you are!</div>
